cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MA, cs.SY, cs.MM

The paper discusses the feasibility of simultaneous information and energy transfer in LTE-A small cell networks, which involves topics related to network infrastructure, wireless communication, and energy harvesting. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves information theory and signal processing, which are related to cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of mathematical models and analysis suggests a possible fit with cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
